msgid ""
"The code in the examples shown in the previous sections explicitly created "
"the content of the email message, by using methods calls such as "
"`message.setText(..)`. This is fine for simple cases, and it is okay in the "
"context of the aforementioned examples, where the intent was to show you the "
"very basics of the API."
msgstr ""

